We'll fix all of our,
that's an ancient

00:10:10.190 --> 00:10:11.410
Gaelic word, I think.

00:10:11.410 --> 00:10:16.560
Lengh.

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:22.190
So now, let me show you that
