00:10:22.190 --> 00:10:25.830
It's especially exaggerated if
maybe I shift this little

00:10:25.830 --> 00:10:30.440
interval dx over to the
right-hand end.

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:32.450
And you can see that the
little portion that

00:10:32.450 --> 00:10:35.930
corresponds to it, which is
the d theta piece, has a

00:10:35.930 --> 00:10:39.130
different length from
