of the function.

00:11:24.390 --> 00:11:27.480
That's the integral, but now
where does theta range?

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:32.430
This time, theta goes
from 0 to pi.

00:11:32.430 --> 00:11:34.990
So the integral is
from 0 to pi.

00:11:34.990 --> 00:11:40.140
And the thing we divide
