00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:47.410
Which is sin theta.

00:11:47.410 --> 00:11:48.680
In terms of theta, of course.

00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:51.710
It's the same as square root of
- x^2, but it's expressed

00:11:51.710 --> 00:11:53.360
