00:30:28.100 --> 00:30:34.800
is Celsius, times
cubic meters.

00:30:34.800 --> 00:30:36.570
These are the correct units.

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:43.760
And now, I can translate this
into Celsius is spelled with a

00:30:43.760 --> 00:30:44.896
C. That's interesting.

00:30:44.896 --> 00:30:46.630
Celsius.

00:30:46.630 --> 00:30:49.840
I can translate this into
